Muscle-specific measures

Source: R/data.R
MUSCLES.Rd

A data.frame containing muscle-type specific measures taken from medial gastrocnemius (MG), lateral gastroc (LG), plantaris (PL), and soleus (SOL): terminal muscle mass, mean cross-sectional area (CSA), glycogen, capillary contacts, and citrate synthase.

MUSCLES

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 1116 rows and 11 columns.

See also

MUSCLES_EMM, MUSCLES_STATS

Examples

print.data.frame(head(MUSCLES))
